headline: Williams-Sonoma (WSM) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of kitchenware and home goods retailer Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) jumped 3.7% in the morning session after an analyst upgrade and fresh data that showed an unexpected rebound in U.S. retail sales, signaling consumer spending remained resilient.
